<br>
If your like I was at your lvl (read: poor as hell), then you can camp the crystal spider eyes, drops in Velks.  Mainly might want to save whatever cash you have for gems if your guild doesn't have extras for Skyshrine gear.  Thats what I figure will be your best choice.  If you're having problems getting SS, throw a group together and hit Kael.  Manor (Icehouse depending on server), and bank camps can drop Thurg quest pieces, of Arena if you have enough.<br>
<br>
